sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User (Teams)
  participant T as TS Teams Adapter
  participant R as Rust Agent Core
  participant P as Policy Engine
  participant G as Microsoft Graph
  participant A as Audit Log

  U->>T: "Summarize unread emails from today"
  T->>R: SendActivity(ActivityEnvelope: request_id, correlation_id, text)
  R->>P: Evaluate(read_mail_summary)
  P-->>R: allow(policy_code=READ_ALLOWED)
  R->>G: GET /me/mailFolders/inbox/messages?$filter=isRead eq false
  alt Graph success
    G-->>R: email headers + ids
    R->>R: LLM summarize (no side effects)
    R->>A: write AuditEvent(action=mail_read_summary, result=success)
    R-->>T: AgentResponse(summary + actions)
    T-->>U: Summary card + buttons
  else Graph transient failure
    G-->>R: 429/503
    R->>A: write AuditEvent(action=mail_read_summary, result=retryable_error)
    R-->>T: AgentResponse(fallback message, retry suggestion)
    T-->>U: "Could not fetch now, please retry"
  end
